</caption>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,1562,2021]" pageId="3" pageNumber="396">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,382,1562,1588]" pageId="3" pageNumber="396">Measurements.</emphasis>
AL: 4.7–5.6; Pfl: 1.3–1.5; MsfL: 1.8–2; MtfL: 2.4–2.5; CeL: 0.11; MgL: 0.28–0.3; FgL: 1–1.1 (ovipositor), 0.7–0.8 (valves); MWh: 2.3–2.4; TL: 12–13.5. Higher values always for males.
</paragraph>
